<http://drug.uk/usage/pregnancy/7a62de41-0e97-413b-bf3d-a079fe20614a> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Statins should be avoided in pregnancy (discontinue 3 months before attempting to conceive) as congenital anomalies have been reported and the decreased synthesis of cholesterol possibly affects fetal development. null" .
