<http://drug.uk/usage/renal-impairment/a427cd7b-c1aa-457c-8f70-6d8f98cbf940> <http://drug.uk/model/patientCondition> "RenalImpairment" .
<http://drug.uk/usage/renal-impairment/a427cd7b-c1aa-457c-8f70-6d8f98cbf940> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> " Dose adjustments\nIn chronic kidney disease, for primary and secondary prevention of cardiovascular events [unlicensed starting dose in primary prevention; unlicensed in secondary prevention], initially 20 mg once daily, increased if necessary (on specialist advice if eGFR < 30 mL/minute/1.73 m^2\n); max. 80 mg once daily." .
